The Government's Decisions:
In the context of development and research of Homeopathy and teaching of Homeopathy in the state.
To advise the Government, the Government may take a decision in this regard. Configuring under 29/06/2022
The Homeopathy Advisory Committee is being reconstituted as follows: -
The functions of the said Committee shall be as follows: -
i. Development and research of Homeopathy, Homoeopathy education in the State.
advice to the government.
